#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Benutzung"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The most common way to run <command>meinproc5</command> is simply as "
#| "<literallayout>\n"
#| "<userinput><command>meinproc5</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
#| "replaceable>\n"
#| "</userinput>\n"
#| "</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
#| "index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. "
#| "Note that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
#| "&konqueror;)."
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"Der meist genutzte Aufruf von <command>meinproc5</command> sieht ganz "
"einfach so aus: <literallayout><userinput><command>meinproc5</command> "
"<replaceable>Docbook-Datei</replaceable></userinput></literallayout>, wobei "
"es sich bei der <replaceable>Docbook-Datei</replaceable> zumeist um die "
"Datei index.docbook handelt. Mit diesem Aufruf werden &HTML;-Dateien "
"erzeugt. Beachten Sie bitte, dass Sie die so erzeugten Dateien nur mit &kde;-"
"basierten Browsern wie z. B. &konqueror; betrachten können."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
#| "you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
#| "<userinput><command>meinproc5</command> --stylesheet "
#| "<replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
#| "replaceable>\n"
#| "</userinput>\n"
#| "</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
#| "full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
#| "kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
#| "produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
#| "command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
#| "<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Wenn die erzeugten &HTML;-Dateien auch mit anderen Browsern betrachtet "
"werden sollen (z. B. weil die Dateien im Internet veröffentlicht werden "
"sollen), so verwenden Sie den Aufruf "
"<literallayout><userinput><command>meinproc5</command> --stylesheet "
"<replaceable>stylesheet-Name</replaceable> <replaceable>Docbook-Datei</"
"replaceable></userinput></literallayout>, wobei es sich bei "
"<replaceable>stylesheet-Name</replaceable> um den vollständigen Pfad zu "
"einem der &XSL;-Stilvorlagen im Ordner &lt;kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/"
"share/kf5/kdoctools/customization handelt. Um brauchbare Ausgaben für die "
"Internet-Veröffentlichung zu erhalten, können Sie beispielsweise die "
"Stilvorlage <command>kde-web.xsl</command> oder <command>kde-chunk-online."
"xsl</command> verwenden. In der <filename>README</filename>-Datei im "
"gleichen Ordner finden Sie weitere Details."

